{"tid":2365491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧：審查、覺醒、政治正確，披著道德正確外衣的專制主義","createTime":"2021-01-13T21:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T08:18:21.000Z","uid":256837,"like":120,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"075506e8000e3cd9e57f63072deb270f9bbb7c6a","tid":2365491,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T21:39:59.000Z","msg":"國務卿蓬佩奧： 審查、覺醒、政治正確，所有行為都指向同一個方向 &mdash; 披著道德正確的外衣專制主義。 身為美國人，是時候讓這樣的所謂覺醒主義沉睡。<br />\n<br />\nCensorship, wokeness, political correctness, it all points in one direction &ndash; authoritarianism, cloaked as moral righteousness. It&rsquo;s not who we are as Americans. It&rsquo;s time that we simply put woke-ism to sleep.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nikki_miumiu/status/1349466730528088064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnikki_miumiu%2Fstatus%2F1349466730528088064&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=cbddaad1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnikki_miumiu%2Fstatus%2F1349466730528088064&h=f9029501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nikki_miumiu/status/1349466730528088064</a>"},{"pid":"0be36a12c98efa34a3b227b2825fded69e6f08c0","tid":2365491,"uid":256837,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T21:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGus4Cg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGus4Cg.png&h=aac7c49d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc2b0e3fc82d89d7fe700ed9b34ffd9df392cacb","tid":2365491,"uid":17103,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T22:00:39.000Z","msg":"叫班撚樣咁撚鍾意中國就強制學習近代史睇下班撚樣仲講唔講政治正確。見到自己嘅批鬥行為同大陸仔一樣，最後係鬥老豆老母先生甚至知識分子。"},{"pid":"785facf631e91e7af8c9ca70a7afbed15cceb8d6","tid":2365491,"uid":256837,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T22:06:55.000Z","msg":"多謝蓬佩奧，大家記得follow佢私人twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hk